.Dd $Mdocdate: September 8 2021 $
.Dt BRGPHY 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm brgphy
.Nd Broadcom BCM54xx/BCM57xx 10/100/1Gb/2.5Gb Ethernet PHY
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "brgphy* at mii?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver supports Broadcom BCM5400 100/1000TX Ethernet PHY interfaces, as well
as the BCM5401, BCM541x, BCM5421, BCM54K2, BCM5462, BCM546x, BCM570x, BCM5714,
BCM5722, BCM575x, BCM5761, BCM578x, BCM5906 and BCM57780 10/100/1000baseT
Ethernet PHY interfaces, and BCM5708S Gigabit/2500 Ethernet PHY interfaces.
